<h3>Registration/User Names</h3><br>
<p>By registering on the Schooldays.ie website, registered users can participate in our online Discussion Forums, surveys,  comment on news stories and receive updates on specific schools.  Care should be taken when selecting a 'User Name' on registration as usernames are displayed beside posts/comments and you may not wish to be identifiable.  For this reason, if you are registering with a view to participating on discussion boards,  it may be more appropriate to select a user name such as 'Butterfly123' or 'Mumof7' etc rather than using your own name.  
<p>We also recommend that when posting comments, childminding ads etc, that you do not post details of your mobile phone number but rather ask respondents to PM (private message) you with their contact details. <a href="https://www.schooldays.ie/articles/Schooldays-Privacy-Policy">View the Schooldays.ie Privacy Policy here</a>
<p><br>
<h3>Forums and public communication</h3><br>
